structure Reference where
  aliases  : Array RefIdent := #[]
  stx      : Syntax
  info     : Info
structure RefInfo where
  definition : Option Reference
def empty : RefInfo := ⟨none, #[]⟩
def addRef (i : RefInfo) (ref : Reference) : RefInfo :=
  match i, ref with
  | { definition := none, .. }
